DESCRIPTION:<p>We’re holding a working bee to help refresh the playground w
 ith new sand and soft fall (tan bark)\, and we’d love your help!</p><p>The 
 main job will be wheelbarrowing sand and tan bark into the play areas from 
 the car park and spreading it evenly. It’s a straightforward but hands-on t
 ask — many hands will make light work.</p><p><strong>What to bring:</strong
 ></p><ul><li><p>Gloves</p></li><li><p>Closed-toe shoes</p></li><li><p>Hat &
 amp\; sunscreen (manifesting the sun)</p></li><li><p>Wheelbarrow (if you ha
 ve one and can bring it)</p></li></ul><p>Children are welcome to attend.</p
 ><p>Even an hour of your time makes a big difference to our kinder communit
 y. Let’s get stuck in and improve the space for our kids to enjoy!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T104706Z
LOCATION:Kallista Kindergarten\, 2 Church St\, Kallista VIC 3791\, Australi
 a
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kallista Kinder Working Bee
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
