DESCRIPTION:<p>We’re excited to invite the special “grand people” in our ch
 ildren’s lives to join us for a morning at kinder!</p><p>Grandpeoples Day i
 s a chance for children to share their kinder world with someone important 
 to them — this might be a grandparent\, great-grandparent\, older relative\
 , family friend\, or another special adult who plays a grand role in their 
 life.</p><p>On the day\, visitors will:</p><ul><li><p>Spend time playing al
 ongside the children</p></li><li><p>See the learning spaces in action</p></
 li><li><p>Join in activities and enjoy some shared moments together</p></li
 ></ul><p>We recognise that every family looks different\, and not all child
 ren have grandparents close by. Each child is welcome to invite a special o
 lder adult who feels like a “grand person” to them.</p><p>We look forward t
 o celebrating the wonderful connections across generations and the importan
 t people who support and love our kinder kids. </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T105920Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kallista Crayfish -  Grandpeoples day
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
