DESCRIPTION:<p>We’re celebrating Book Week at kinder and inviting children 
 to join the fun by coming dressed as a character from their favourite book.
 </p><p>Children are encouraged to:</p><ul><li><p>Dress up as a much-loved s
 tory character (simple costumes are perfect!)</p></li><li><p>Bring along th
 eir favourite book to share with the group</p></li><li><p>Talk about why th
 ey enjoy the story and characters</p></li></ul><p>Throughout the day\, we’l
 l enjoy book-themed activities\, storytelling\, and plenty of opportunities
  to celebrate a love of reading together.</p><p>Costumes do not need to be 
 elaborate — creativity and comfort are key. Please ensure outfits are suita
 ble for active play and easy for children to manage independently.</p><p>We
  look forward to seeing all the wonderful characters come to life at kinder
 !</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T111047Z
LOCATION:Kallista Kindergarten\, 2 Church St\, Kallista VIC 3791\, Australi
 a
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kallista Kinder Book Week! Dress as your fav character
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
