DESCRIPTION:<br><article dir="auto"><br><br><br><div dir="auto"><br><br><p>
 Join us for a fun-filled trivia night to raise funds for our kinder!</p><p>
 <strong>When:</strong> Saturday\, from 7:00pm onwards<br><strong>Where:</st
 rong> Kallista Primary School Hall<br><strong>Theme:</strong> Movie Charact
 ers (dress up encouraged!)</p><p>Enjoy trivia rounds\, games\, puzzles\, do
 or prizes\, and a silent auction — all while supporting the kinder. Gather 
 a team of 8 and come along for a great night out or meet new friends and be
  placed on the night!<br><br>Tickets and childcare essential as this is an 
 over 18 event.</p></article>
