DESCRIPTION:<p>Our kinder is hosting a Book Fair sponsored by Scholastic to
  raise funds for new equipment and upgrades to benefit all of our children.
 </p><p>Throughout the week\, a range of books will be available to purchase
 . Brochures will be sent home and extra copies will be available at the kin
 der for families to browse together and choose their favourites.</p><p><str
 ong>How it works:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Browse the brochure with your chil
 d and select any books you’d like to purchase.</p></li><li><p>Follow the or
 dering instructions provided in the brochure.</p></li><li><p>Books will be 
 delivered back to the kinder for distribution.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Ever
 y purchase makes a difference — 100% of proceeds go directly to the kinder<
 /strong>\, helping fund learning resources\, play equipment\, and improveme
 nts to our environment.</p><p>Thank you for supporting our kinder and helpi
 ng foster a love of reading while giving back to the community!<br></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T105421Z
LOCATION:Kallista Kindergarten\, 2 Church St\, Kallista VIC 3791\, Australi
 a
