DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us as we mark the Winter Solstice with a cosy community
  celebration in the area in front of the kinder.</p><p>As the longest night
  of the year arrives\, we’ll come together to share warmth\, light\, and co
 nnection with relaxed\, family-friendly festivities.</p><p><strong>What to 
 expect:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lantern-making activity for children (and gr
 own-ups!)</p></li><li><p>Gentle solstice-themed activities and space to gat
 her together</p></li><li><p>Warm drinks such as mulled wine and cider (non-
 alcoholic options available)</p></li><li><p>Dinner provided — we’re plannin
 g to share pizzas during the evening</p></li><li><p>Time to connect with ot
 her families while the children play</p></li></ul><p><strong>Time:</strong>
  4:00pm – 8:00pm<br>Families are welcome to drop in for part or all of the 
 evening.</p><p><strong>What to bring:</strong></p><ul><li><p>A warm jacket 
 and weather-appropriate clothing</p></li><li><p>A reusable mug if you’d lik
 e one for hot drinks</p></li><li><p>Picnic rug or camp chair (optional)</p>
 </li></ul><p>Children must remain supervised by their attending adult at al
 l times.</p><p>We hope this will be a relaxed and welcoming way to embrace 
 the winter season together as a kinder community.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T110601Z
LOCATION:Kallista Kindergarten\, 2 Church St\, Kallista VIC 3791\, Australi
 a
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kallista Kinder - Winter Solstice Event
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
