DESCRIPTION:<p>A professional photographer (Amber) will be visiting the kin
 der to take individual children’s photos during kinder sessions including b
 ush kinder from March 16th - 19th.</p><p><strong>Important:</strong> Photos
  are <strong>not automatic</strong>. If you would like your child photograp
 hed\, you must complete Amber’s online booking form and make payment direct
 ly through her system.</p><p>When booking\, please provide:</p><ul><li><p>Y
 our child’s full name</p></li><li><p>The day(s) your child attends kinder</
 p></li><li><p>Your contact details</p></li><li><p>Confirmation of your sele
 cted package/payment</p></li></ul><p>Only children who are booked and paid 
 for through Amber’s online form will be photographed.</p><p>If you do not c
 omplete the booking form\, your child will not be included on the day.</p><
 p>Please complete your booking before the cut-off date to secure your spot.
 </p>
